          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1641896130674-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the baking tray from the oven</p><p>Add one rasher of <strong>smoked streaky bacon</strong> to each ciabatta base (leave the <strong>remaining rashers </strong>on the tray) and layer 4 <strong>cheddar flavour slices</strong> on top</p><p>Add both the <strong>ciabatta</strong> <strong>bases</strong> and <strong>lids</strong> (cut side up) to the other side of the tray, then return the tray to the oven for 5-6 min or until the cheeze has melted</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p>",
